author: Peta Fuller
title: What are 'wet markets' and why you've probably shopped at one
description: Coronavirus is placing wet markets under heavy scrutiny as China begins reopening them. So what exactly are they?
content:
Posted 
April 17, 2020 18:44:37
Wet markets have been forever linked to coronavirus, thanks to those early cases at Wuhan's Huanan Seafood Market last year.
